== Personal life ==
In 2007, Brannigan was [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nh0AC0auV9s featured in a segment] on the TV show ''[[Inside Edition]]'' and in an article in ''[[The New York Times]]'', both of which covered the growing demand for [[tattoo removal]] in the U.S.<ref name="NY Times â Erasing Tattoos">{{cite news|last=Singer|first=Natasha|title=Erasing Tattoos, Out of Regret or for a New Canvas|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/17/us/17tattoo.html|accessdate=25 September 2011|newspaper=The New York Times|date=17 June 2007}}</ref>
Brannigan currently lives in the greater Los Angeles area.<ref name="NY Times â Erasing Tattoos" />
